com.aylanetworks.agilelink.framework

类 AccountSettings

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.aylanetworks.agilelink.framework.AccountSettings

  • public class AccountSettings
extends java.lang.Object
    AccountSettings is a class used to store and retrieve information related to the user's account, but not part of the AylaUser object. Currently the class stores the following information:
    • The selected notification types for device status: Push, SMS and Email
    • The contact ID of the owner

    The AccountSettings object can be retrieved from the server using tht static method fetchAccountSettings(com.aylanetworks.agilelink.framework.AccountSettings.AccountSettingsCallback). This method will fetch the latest AccountSettings information from the server and return an initialized AccountSettings object to the callback.

    The SessionManager fetches the AccountSettings from the server after login. This can be accessed via SessionManager#getAccountSettings().

    • 方法详细资料

      • fetchAccountSettings

        public static void fetchAccountSettings(AccountSettings.AccountSettingsCallback callback)
        Fetches the account settings from the server. The callback is called with an initialized AccountSettings object, or null if an error occurred.
        参数:
        callback - Callback called when the settings have been retrieved from the server

      • pushToServer

        public void pushToServer(AccountSettings.AccountSettingsCallback callback)
        Updates data on the server with the current AccountSettings information.
        参数:
        callback - Callback called when the settings have been updated.

      • getNotificationTypes

        public java.util.List<AylaServiceApp.NotificationType> getNotificationTypes()
        Returns a list of notification types that are enabled for this account. This list can include one or more of:
        • com.aylanetworks.agilelink.framework.DeviceNotificationHelper#NOTIFICATION_METHOD_EMAIL
        • com.aylanetworks.agilelink.framework.DeviceNotificationHelper#NOTIFICATION_METHOD_PUSH
        • com.aylanetworks.agilelink.framework.DeviceNotificationHelper#NOTIFICATION_METHOD_SMS
        返回:
        an array of Strings representing the enabled device notification types for this account

      • addNotificationMethod

        public void addNotificationMethod(AylaServiceApp.NotificationType notificationMethod)
        Adds the specified notification method to the user's preferences. Note that this only stores the information and does not update any device notifications on the devices themselves.

        Callers should call the pushToServer(com.aylanetworks.agilelink.framework.AccountSettings.AccountSettingsCallback) method in order to persist changes to AccountSettings once all local updates have been made.

        参数:
        notificationMethod - The notification method. One of:
        • DeviceNotificationHelper#NOTIFICATION_METHOD_PUSH
        • DeviceNotificationHelper#NOTIFICATION_METHOD_EMAIL
        • DeviceNotificationHelper#NOTIFICATION_METHOD_SMS

      • removeNotificationMethod

        public void removeNotificationMethod(AylaServiceApp.NotificationType notificationMethod)
        Removes the supplied notification method from the list of enabled notification methods.

        Callers should call the pushToServer(com.aylanetworks.agilelink.framework.AccountSettings.AccountSettingsCallback) method in order to persist changes to AccountSettings once all local updates have been made.

        参数:
        notificationMethod - Notification method to set (PUSH | EMAIL | SMS)

      • isNotificationMethodSet

        public boolean isNotificationMethodSet(AylaServiceApp.NotificationType notificationMethod)
        Returns true if the supplied notification method is set on the user's account.
        参数:
        notificationMethod - String of the notification method to test
        返回:
        true if the method is set, or false if not

        public java.lang.Integer getOwnerContactID()
